    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a legal requirement for former employers to provide a reference",
        "additional_details": "It effects people's paths to work. If an old employer refuses or ignores giving a reference it could potentially lose them a job. Especially in the healthcare industry.",
        "background": "When a person goes for a new job, an old employer must give the new employer a reference to confirm dates worked.",
